[{"id":1133697,"node":"小米","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/xiaomi","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_mini.png?m=1584400459","description":"前一段时间联想的自研芯片用到了自家平板上，根据评测性能也还不错。<br />联想的这款芯片宣传很少，当时想可能是中美敏感期不好宣传。<br />没想到才过几天小米芯片出来后到处宣传。<br /><br />考虑到小米有松果的前科，不知道玄戒 O1 里面有多少东西是小米自己的。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133697","replies":203,"created_ts":1747963213,"created":"09:20:13","title":"玄戒 O1 有多少东西是小米自己的","author":"vicalloy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/vicalloy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7c82/fab8/1293_mini.png?m=1730723648"},{"id":1133688,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598","description":"从 win 转 mac ，macmini m4 高强度使用半年了，睡眠发热这个问题始终无法解决，待机温度能达到 60 多度，给 macmini 连了个小米插座，睡眠功耗比正常使用还高，这你受得了？一开始我还上网搜解决方案，什么看功耗的软件不要用，什么设置里防止自动进入睡眠，什么活动监视器查看哪个程序耗电等等，基本上各种方法都用过了，平常没事就打开米家插头看看它功耗多少，毫无意外，完全玄学，纯看心情，没有任何规律，功耗一会低一会高。<br /><br />而且最最重要的是内存泄露问题，煞笔 windowsever 这玩意几天不关机，直接占用了好几个 g 内存，光是吐槽 windowsever 的贴子我在站里都看到不下十个了，但是没有任何解决办法，别问，问就是重启，既然要没事就看看内存占用还要重启还不如不用的时候就关机，苹果用户是真的适应能力强，说到这我又要顺便吐槽一下 homepod ，前两天音箱坏了，家里有两台 homepod 想给 mac 当个音箱都不行，那延迟真是日了狗了。<br /><br />说回 macmini 来，上个星期时开始，每次用完就关机，戒掉了没事就要看看功耗的恶习，机身冰冰凉，开机的时候摸着也轻松无压力，还是怎么舒服怎么用。如果有任何手段可以解决发热和内存泄露的问题，我还是愿意不关机的。关键这两个问题很普遍，我在网上看到不仅是 macmini ，mac studio ，MacBook 都有，只能说 macos 不尽如人意的地方还很多。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133688","replies":161,"created_ts":1747961229,"created":"08:47:09","title":"不懂，那些说 mac 不用关机的，难道都不发热么？","author":"xtx","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xtx","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1266/8b36/439903_mini.png?m=1743131645"},{"id":1133699,"node":"投资","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706","description":"之前美股亏了不少钱，后面继续借钱玩期权幻想暴富翻身，结果玩 0 date 期权又亏没了 10w 。最近每次晚上开单的时候总是感觉的特别紧张，发慌，后背发凉，亏钱了总想快速赚回来，一把 all  in 干，结果可想而知，亏没了。事后可是心里很不心甘，自残，很焦虑，很忧愁。作为三十多岁的人，回首过去，一事无成，负债累累，每天晚上失眠，焦虑的不行，真的不知道未来的路该怎么走。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133699","replies":152,"created_ts":1747963365,"created":"09:22:45","title":"这个月美股又亏了 10w，好难受😣","author":"luck2023","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/luck2023","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/daa09f726c0b722fa89f5baceb898c55?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":1133729,"node":"汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960","description":"<p>现法拉利 er ，前小米 er 说一句：雷总不管进入哪个行业，都会把这行卷到不赚钱👍。抄袭的是中国人，被卷死的也是中国人。大企业家，贱人贱己贱行业。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/MRzwMVGI.jpeg\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133729","replies":149,"created_ts":1747966482,"created":"10:14:42","title":"现法拉利 er，前小米 er 说一句","author":"t4we","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/t4we","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f85de639bb82e0f83cbf419a15fbb947?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":1133797,"node":"小米","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/xiaomi","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_mini.png?m=1584400459","description":"<p><a href=\"https://newsroom.arm.com/blog/xiaomi-xring-o1-arm-silicon-launch\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://newsroom.arm.com/blog/xiaomi-xring-o1-arm-silicon-launch</a></p>\n<p>现在进去已经是 page not  found</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/djtVQ3D.png\"/></p>\n<p>还好有人截图了</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sQuklMU.jpeg\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133797","replies":121,"created_ts":1747976369,"created":"12:59:29","title":"没想到 ARM 删帖来的这么快，是真相了么","author":"goodryb","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/goodryb","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5a60/ef6c/110971_mini.png?m=1711524398"},{"id":1133760,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1727584731","description":"<p>我之前还想着上网站了，在线看看，我看到诸如爱奇艺，腾讯视频前段时间都开启预约了，结果来了个大的</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20250521A076O100\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20250521A076O100</a></p>\n<p>可能是现阶段实在没有能打的影片吧，不理解只能尊重了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133760","replies":118,"created_ts":1747969313,"created":"11:01:53","title":"唉，哪吒 2 又延期到 6 月 30 号了，这是闹哪样呀","author":"ansnail","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ansnail","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1501/f964/480068_mini.png?m=1745458381"},{"id":1133883,"node":"小米","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/xiaomi","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_mini.png?m=1584400459","description":"每当论坛里面讨论小米汽车，就会吵起来，都不能客观理性的交流。。<br /><br />觉得有一定的原因：是小米的宣传方式太夸张了，渐渐的影响个人判断。对于公司来说必然是好的，但是对于消费者来说不一定是好的：<br /><br />1. 混淆了个人判断。有部分消费者是没有个人判断，听到宣传之后就无脑冲了，冲了之后就无条件相信夸大宣传的部分导致造成了严重的事故。<br /><br />2. 这种夸张的宣传给整个行业带来的印象不太好，车这种东西不应该像手机这样宣传。如果各个厂商都这样宣传，消费者真的会被搞的头大吧？<br /><br />3. 搞得有点像传教一样了，讨论小米汽车和其他品牌的汽车完全不一样的风格。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133883","replies":108,"created_ts":1747991775,"created":"17:16:15","title":"小米汽车是不是舆论造势太过了？","author":"HiShan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/HiShan","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c2c2/bb90/277270_mini.png?m=1741676511"},{"id":1133758,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425","description":"<p>想想我本来也是能开上迈巴赫 480 ，只是...出了点插曲\n现实中 20w 的车都没开上</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133758","replies":103,"created_ts":1747969103,"created":"10:58:23","title":"买房亏掉的钱够你买什么车了","author":"Duanye7X24","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Duanye7X24","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3db51fffa722a5da5d24bb9797072038?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":1133928,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1727584731","description":"<p>参考知乎讨论  <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/1909186314550609183\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/1909186314550609183</a></p>\n<p>你一言我一语的基本拼凑出真相了：</p>\n<p>小米玄戒 o1 是 Arm CSS 服务（ Neoverse Compute Subsystems ）的首款手机 SOC 芯片，CSS 方式是针对一些“尽快上马“的场景，在这个授权方式下，ARM 可以帮厂商完成 ARM+第三方 P 的整合，相当于 SoC 级别的整合在很大程度上都是 ARM 协助的。</p>\n<p>这和传统的 IP 授权有很大的差异，就像要做饺子（ SOC ），原来 ARM 是提供面粉和鸡蛋（ IP 授权服务），现在直接是预制菜半成品（ CSS 服务），可以供你的蒸、煮、煎各种不同的使用场景。</p>\n<p>这种情况下，大大缩短芯片流片流程，但是费用也会高很多，也就是利润和技术的大头都是由 ARM 获得和实现的。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>离谱的是，现在相关信息被疯狂捂嘴，arm 原来的首页文章被删除，国内也没有任何相关大博主能讨论相关信息。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>预测我的这个帖子，要么上不了首页；</p>\n<p><strong>要么马上会有故意说引战言论的人，让帖子光速拉入水深火热</strong></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133928","replies":98,"created_ts":1748008085,"created":"21:48:05","title":"案子破了，小米 135 亿研发玄戒 o1 的真实情况","author":"digd","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/digd","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b0ce8a14b47d39fc5dfebd678e47c47c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":1133693,"node":"git","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/git","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ec89/5663/102_mini.png?m=1589292852","description":"<pre><code>git cp：没这号命令😂\ngit mv：这是改名\n</code></pre>\n<p>比如已有 a.txt ，我现在要个 b.txt 。 如何复制出 b.txt 这个文件，并且复制前的历史和 a.txt 保持一致？</p>\n<p>还是说 和空文件夹 一样，git 不在乎你死活？</p>\n<p>操作尽量简单，要是涉及的非基础知识点太多，还是算了，这历史不要也罢😂</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133693","replies":98,"created_ts":1747962822,"created":"09:13:42","title":"问个 Git 基操：怎么样复制一个文件，能保持历史记录？","author":"xiangyuecn","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiangyuecn","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd8e/d2e9/225735_mini.png?m=1521809562"},{"id":1133778,"node":"电动汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ev","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_mini.png?m=1643940920","description":"<p>近半年一直在关注纯电 SUV 领域，YU7 总算出来了。目前决赛圈极氪 7X 、Model Y 、YU7 ，三者各有优劣。有一起想冲 YU7 的老哥老姐不</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1133778","replies":92,"created_ts":1747971765,"created